00:38:30,450 --> 00:38:32,840
Gosh, was she rewarded a certificate for this?

560
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,340
She must have one for being

561
00:38:34,340 --> 00:38:35,830
the most snide and despicable.

562
00:38:36,310 --> 00:38:38,200
Then why are you going?

563
00:38:40,980 --> 00:38:42,030
Yeonseo.

564
00:38:42,030 --> 00:38:43,440
Don't talk to me. You're too loud.

565
00:38:53,870 --> 00:38:56,160
Blessed are those who have patience.

566
00:38:57,700 --> 00:39:00,120
This foolish one may not be aware as of now,

567
00:39:00,590 --> 00:39:02,750
but she will appreciate you one day.

568
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:07,820
She will cry and regret her past actions.

569
00:39:10,770 --> 00:39:12,160
Give it to me. Where is it?

570
00:39:43,270 --> 00:39:44,380
Yeonseo!

571
00:39:46,980 --> 00:39:48,950
I'm so glad that my niece is here!

572
00:39:51,590 --> 00:39:53,300
You two are in big trouble.

573
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:55,810
This foolish one has no patience for you.

574
00:39:57,310 --> 00:39:58,630
Watch out for her stick.

575
00:39:59,770 --> 00:40:01,310
Have you been well?

576
00:40:01,310 --> 00:40:03,290
Of course, of course.

577
00:40:03,290 --> 00:40:06,550
We've cried so much, wanting to see you.

578
00:40:07,080 --> 00:40:09,370
You never met us for the past three years.

579
00:40:09,410 --> 00:40:10,730
But today, you're here.

580
00:40:10,730 --> 00:40:13,240
Your parents must be proud of you.

581
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:14,470
This is great.

582
00:40:14,470 --> 00:40:17,640
Our guests are very high-minded,

583
00:40:17,640 --> 00:40:20,200
