586
00:40:23,540 --> 00:40:24,820
It will make you look more tragic.

587
00:40:25,610 --> 00:40:27,710
The rich tend to spend money

588
00:40:27,980 --> 00:40:29,790
when they feel a sense of superiority.

589
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:33,120
Mom, that's enough.

590
00:40:34,450 --> 00:40:35,810
Please understand.

591
00:40:36,380 --> 00:40:38,230
As the general director of the ballet company,

592
00:40:38,230 --> 00:40:40,970
