593
00:40:41,530 --> 00:40:42,590
Runa.

594
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,380
You remember my voice.

595
00:40:47,910 --> 00:40:49,020
I'm glad you're here.

596
00:40:49,330 --> 00:40:50,550
Let's go in.

597
00:40:50,550 --> 00:40:53,980
