00:41:24,610 --> 00:41:26,410
Nina. Good luck.

602
00:41:27,340 --> 00:41:28,340
You can do it.

603
00:41:33,940 --> 00:41:35,030
You're the best.

604
00:41:35,380 --> 00:41:37,230
The prima ballerina of Fantasia

605
00:41:37,850 --> 00:41:40,010
is only you, Nina.

606
00:41:40,530 --> 00:41:41,770
