623
00:43:03,350 --> 00:43:04,880
Call her, "Ms. Lee."

624
00:43:05,630 --> 00:43:08,710
By the way, I don't understand why she came

625
00:43:08,710 --> 00:43:10,430
when she's blind.

626
00:43:10,700 --> 00:43:11,790
