00:47:31,160 --> 00:47:33,200
I've been looking for her, but I can't find her.

640
00:47:34,300 --> 00:47:35,560
She'll be here soon.

641
00:47:35,560 --> 00:47:37,280
It's been three years, you know.

642
00:47:38,830 --> 00:47:39,800
Yeonseo.

