648
00:47:56,340 --> 00:47:58,490
She's the only daughter of the first chairman.

649
00:47:58,490 --> 00:48:01,220
Hey, we have to get him to shut his mouth first.

650
00:48:01,220 --> 00:48:02,230
Go.

651
00:48:02,230 --> 00:48:04,080
We have invited Ms. Lee Yeonseo.

652
00:48:05,620 --> 00:48:06,760
Give her a warm welcome.

653
00:48:08,090 --> 00:48:09,540
It's been three years.

654
00:48:09,540 --> 00:48:12,170
The daughter of Fantasia. The madonna of Fantasia.

655
00:48:12,170 --> 00:48:15,120
Where are you, Ms. Lee Yeonseo?

656
00:49:11,300 --> 00:49:13,290
Hello, I'm Lee Yeonseo.

657
00:49:14,120 --> 00:49:16,070
Today is a special day.

658
00:49:16,140 --> 00:49:18,270
