660
00:49:22,700 --> 00:49:24,730
I've given a lot of thought

661
00:49:25,000 --> 00:49:26,480
on how to celebrate this occasion.

662
00:49:27,290 --> 00:49:28,390
I thought about showing up

663
00:49:28,390 --> 00:49:30,000
as a corpse by hanging myself in the restroom.

664
00:49:31,770 --> 00:49:33,130
To make a dramatic scene.

665
00:49:35,950 --> 00:49:38,410
I bet everyone is looking at me with pity.

666
00:49:39,730 --> 00:49:41,450
I hope that you can support us

667
00:49:41,760 --> 00:49:43,480
as much as you pity me

668
00:49:43,780 --> 00:49:45,800
and as much as you think that I deserve this.

669
00:49:51,480 --> 00:49:52,490
As you know,

670
00:49:52,490 --> 00:49:54,560
when I was the only principal dancer here,

671
00:49:54,700 --> 00:49:56,900
my dear Geum Nina was my understudy.

672
00:49:56,980 --> 00:49:58,520
In other words, she was my shadow.

673
00:49:59,050 --> 00:50:00,680
If I would get sick

674
00:50:00,680 --> 00:50:02,710
or run away because I fall in love,

675
00:50:02,880 --> 00:50:05,120
her responsibility was to take my place.

676
00:50:05,700 --> 00:50:08,150
Unfortunately, I was too healthy.

677
00:50:08,150 --> 00:50:10,360
And except ballet, I found everything boring.

678
00:50:10,360 --> 00:50:13,120
I've never skipped a performance.

679
00:50:13,960 --> 00:50:14,940
However, when the sun is gone,

680
00:50:14,940 --> 00:50:16,340
the moon is bound to dominate.

681
00:50:16,790 --> 00:50:19,340
