The sunset glow is very beautiful.

742
00:55:23,140 --> 00:55:24,160
It's...

743
00:55:25,880 --> 00:55:27,070
breathtaking.

744
00:55:34,770 --> 00:55:36,050
Let's start getting ready slowly.

745
00:55:36,400 --> 00:55:37,840
You can begin your rehabilitation.

746
00:55:37,840 --> 00:55:39,340
- And the foundation... / - Stop.

747
00:55:40,660 --> 00:55:41,670
Yeonseo.

748
00:55:41,670 --> 00:55:43,300
I told you to stop calling me that!

749
00:55:44,090 --> 00:55:45,330
I hate everything!

750
00:55:45,330 --> 00:55:47,970
I hate ballet, the foundation, everything!

751
00:55:47,970 --> 00:55:49,950
So don't tell me what to do!

752
00:55:54,480 --> 00:55:55,580
Lee Yeonseo!

753
00:55:57,650 --> 00:55:58,660
Did you...

754
00:55:59,660 --> 00:56:01,070
