755
00:56:02,750 --> 00:56:03,900
Pull yourself together.

756
00:56:04,290 --> 00:56:06,000
You're in the middle of a battlefield.

757
00:56:06,360 --> 00:56:08,610
Do you know how many guns are pointed at your heart?

758
00:56:08,610 --> 00:56:10,540
No idea, but I hope I can die at once,

759
00:56:10,540 --> 00:56:11,540
quickly.

760
00:56:11,540 --> 00:56:13,090
And stop saying that you want to die.

761
00:56:14,940 --> 00:56:16,210
We're almost there.

762
00:56:16,480 --> 00:56:19,200
