763
00:56:19,910 --> 00:56:21,980
I will bring you back to your place.

764
00:56:23,340 --> 00:56:24,480
My place?

765
00:56:25,270 --> 00:56:26,340
How?

766
00:56:26,950 --> 00:56:28,180
Are you going to give me eyes?

767
00:56:28,180 --> 00:56:29,710
- Yeonseo. / - Bring me back?

768
00:56:29,710 --> 00:56:31,520
Where? Who says you can? Who do you think you are?

769
00:56:32,270 --> 00:56:33,850
If you act like my dad once again,

770
00:56:34,550 --> 00:56:36,050
I will really fire you.

771
00:57:20,140 --> 00:57:21,250
Mr. Jo.

772
00:57:31,890 --> 00:57:33,880
Yeonseo. Yeonseo, hold tight!

773
00:57:41,580 --> 00:57:44,070
What? What's going on?

774
00:57:44,660 --> 00:57:45,660
Yeonseo.

775
00:58:04,710 --> 00:58:06,080
Gosh, I might be late.

776
00:58:06,470 --> 00:58:07,830
Mr. Jo...

777
00:58:45,200 --> 00:58:46,520
Mr. Jo.

778
00:58:48,310 --> 00:58:49,690
Can you hear me?

779
00:58:51,800 --> 00:58:53,020
Mr. Jo?

780
00:59:13,840 --> 00:59:15,380
Is anybody there?

781
00:59:18,730 --> 00:59:21,050
Help us.

782
00:59:23,790 --> 00:59:26,910
Who knew these flowers were for a funeral?

783
00:59:42,340 --> 00:59:43,450
Rest

784
00:59:44,240 --> 00:59:45,340
