785
00:59:49,970 --> 00:59:51,150
Who's there?

786
00:59:54,980 --> 00:59:55,980
Is...

787
00:59:57,270 --> 00:59:58,620
Is someone there?

788
01:00:01,310 --> 01:00:02,370
Over here.

789
01:00:02,940 --> 01:00:05,450
There are people here. Over here.

790
01:00:07,740 --> 01:00:08,790
Please.

791
01:00:09,230 --> 01:00:11,740
Please help us. Please.

792
01:00:15,350 --> 01:00:16,840
Hey, who are you?

793
01:00:17,550 --> 01:00:19,480
