794
01:00:21,380 --> 01:00:23,360
You jerk.

795
01:00:24,320 --> 01:00:25,770
Don't you have any conscience?

796
01:00:26,340 --> 01:00:28,110
If you ran away because you were scared,

797
01:00:28,680 --> 01:00:30,480
