798
01:00:31,180 --> 01:00:32,280
Sir.

799
01:00:32,730 --> 01:00:34,760
Sir. Hey.

800
01:00:34,760 --> 01:00:37,340
Whoever you are, please...

801
01:00:39,280 --> 01:00:40,730
Why does her voice sound so clear?

802
01:00:58,120 --> 01:00:59,340
Help me.

803
01:01:00,320 --> 01:01:01,590
I can't.

804
01:01:02,250 --> 01:01:04,140
I really can't do anything about human life.

805
01:01:05,160 --> 01:01:07,880
Please. Save me.

806
01:01:09,210 --> 01:01:11,880
I can't. I have no time. I have to go.

807
01:01:13,290 --> 01:01:14,650
I want to live.

808
01:01:16,820 --> 01:01:18,750
I wanted to die every single day,

809
01:01:20,380 --> 01:01:21,790
but I want to live now.

810
01:01:22,840 --> 01:01:24,070
I want to live.

811
01:01:29,050 --> 01:01:30,980
I wanted to die every single day,

812
01:01:33,620 --> 01:01:35,080
but I want to live now.

