01:02:19,860 --> 01:02:22,590
I shouldn't have done that.

814
01:02:24,000 --> 01:02:27,180
I was not supposed to do that.

815
01:02:57,400 --> 01:03:00,740
(Angel's Last Mission: Love)

816
01:03:01,940 --> 01:03:04,920
Like smoke and dust.

817
01:03:07,040 --> 01:03:09,410
Hey, is someone there?

818
01:03:09,490 --> 01:03:10,810
Young lady, were you dreaming?

819
01:03:12,190 --> 01:03:14,700
You must successfully do a mission for 100 days

820
01:03:14,700 --> 01:03:16,500
