01:03:17,500 --> 01:03:19,090
I'm Kim Dan, the interviewee.

823
01:03:19,090 --> 01:03:20,360
I got closer to her.

824
01:03:21,550 --> 01:03:23,360
Why does a secretary have to learn to do this?

825
01:03:23,360 --> 01:03:24,820
Clean up everything.

826
01:03:25,640 --> 01:03:27,500
What is it that I have to do?

827
01:03:28,590 --> 01:03:29,610
Love.

828
01:03:29,610 --> 01:03:31,050
I will make her fall in love.
